{"tid":445767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人難接受間屋「死過人」","createTime":"2017-10-23T16:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T03:41:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"45e1db8b3e0f48706452598abecc6629b9fc6f10","tid":445767,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171023/20191678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F20191678&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6cmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=090371c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F20191678&h=69d8f761\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171023/20191678</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人難接受間屋「死過人」<br />\n<br />\n12,222<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171023/large/a07a03a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171023%2Flarge%2Fa07a03a.gif&h=d067a493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中大及港大為居家照顧支援服務及在家終老的可行性做研究，希望引發社會更多討論。<br />\n<br />\n公立醫院逼爆，為末期病人提供紓緩治療，以及在家寧養安度餘生，將成大勢所趨。中大公共衞生及基層醫療學院及港大社會科學學院，正就前線醫護的培訓及社區支援服務模式研究。參與先導計劃的社工林嘉欣指出，在家善終，爭議仍不少，尤其法律方面的問題亦有待解決。此外，香港人重視樓價，未必太多人接受間屋「死過人」。凡此種種，均令在家善終，未必能如西方社會般「落地」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或被解剖查死因<br />\n<br />\n香港九成人都在醫院過世，臨終時，大有可能還聽到鄰床病人的呻吟、醫生在急救，不想在陌生又冰冷的醫院告別人間，香港人是否有權選擇在家善終？林嘉欣說原則上是有，過往亦確實遇過出院後在家寧養的末期病人，提出希望在家過世的遺願。「坊間有醫生可上門簽發死亡證，不過至少要上門3次，升斗市民唔會好似富豪咁，有私人醫生，執行上係有難度。」<br />\n<br />\n香港並無安樂死，不在醫院死亡，警察一般都會上門調查，皆因就算重病也有機會是他殺，所以，若你臨終的願望是在熟悉的家安詳離世，就要有死後被解剖調查死因的心理準備。此外，香港人重視樓價，未必接受間屋「死過人」，早前有男女跳樓跌落樓下平台單位，網上討論得最熱切的，竟是對樓價的影響。香港人充滿現實主義的另類「核心價值」可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂麗嬋  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n反思親人離世　 社工扶人先扶己<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n理大設智慧城市實驗室　 分析熱島效應"},{"pid":"32a13b4e69d325ea8446df4625283801b2240247","tid":445767,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:11:32.000Z","msg":"香港並無安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113b1e46bb7bfc7945da6e077a2c096b3080c610","tid":445767,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a342546eb4383e86d0dd69d22782b75756797047","tid":445767,"uid":72173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"支持係屋企死<br />\n<br />\n慳床位，樓價跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1384aff13019dbcf37eeca4aa753c59ab1e344","tid":445767,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"以死降低香港樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cc6cc530031248b1b0b1b9935bbc3720507e1a","tid":445767,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以死降低香港樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日有人跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69479b0d243465a6102c482c762f6f763073c07a","tid":445767,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dee1234924c7cd577d4ea444f0f047a0960155","tid":445767,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以死降低香港樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港共政府，用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5a2eef23a9fbbbf8aee642ebe57694e8b1f41c","tid":445767,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"間間小學都亂葬岡你又唔讀？"},{"pid":"f27ee8f5acec16426b8be13979a5417a56b